== Interface Overview

Actuarial Risk Scores/Risk Corridors: Under contract to DHS, MQD’s actuary calculates
Medicaid beneficiary-level risk scores that quantify individuals’ relative risk burden. This
calculation is performed outside of the HPMMIS and is formatted into data tables.

